## DESIGN SYSTEM

Base surfaces follow the app tokens in `frontend/src/styles/globals.css`: deep blacks (`--black-deep`, `--black-panel`, `--black-card`), borders at `rgba(255,255,255,0.08)`, primary white copy, muted grays for secondary text. Tricolor saffron/green and Ashoka blues are used sparingly for institutional cues, not decoration.

Typography uses **Inter** for UI and **JetBrains Mono** for identifiers, codes, and timestamps where a monospace read is required. Prefer semantic contrast and clear hierarchy over decorative gradients on admin routes.

Spacing and layout on admin pages should prioritize scanability: predictable grids, consistent padding scale, and components from existing UI primitives (`Modal`, `Input`, tables) rather than one-off marketing layouts.

